      "n": 37,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Septix Deenas buhſtew\nGalihdsinatchanu darriht pahr\nto Altari/ nn wiꞥſch eefwehtiht/\nun tad buhſ tas * Altaris to\nfwehtu Leetu Swehtiba/ wiſſ/\nkas to Altari aiskarr/ tas taps\nfwehtihts.\n* Tas Altaris nosihme Kristu, kas ta Sweh-\ntiba irr, zaur ko wiſſi fwehtihti tohp, kas winnu\neekſch Tizzibas aiskarr. Luhk: Matt: 23, 19.\nEebr: 13, 10. 1.Kor: 10, 16,17,18.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schis nu irr/ ko tew us\nto Altari buhſ fataisiht/ diwi\nJehrus/ Gadskahrtu wezzus/ ik-\ndeenas allaschin.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 39,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "To weenu Jehru buhſ tew\nRihtā fataifiht/ un ohtru buhſ\ntew fataifiht ap Wakkara Laiku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 40,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ar definitu Teesu Kwee-\nschu-Miltu/ ko buhſ fajaukt ar\nweenu Zettortni no weena Inna\nfagruhſtas Etjes/ un par to\nDserramn-Uppuri weenu Zettort-\nnino weena InnaWiyna/preekſch\nta weena Jehra.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 41,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un to ohtru Jehru buhſ\ntew fataifiht ap Wakkara Laiku/\ntew buhſ ar to darriht/ ittin ka\nar to Ehdamu-Uppuri Rihtā/ un\nka ar winna Dserramn-Uppuri\npar faldn Smarfchu/ tas irr\nweenu Uaguns tam KURGAM.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 42,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schis irr tas deeniskis\nDedsans Uppuris pee juhsu\nPehznahkameem/ pee tahs Sa-\neefchanas Telts Durwinm preekſch\nta KUNGA/ tur buhſ ta Sa-\neefchanas Weeta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 43,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tur buhſ ta Sa-ee-\nfchanas Weeta ar Israēta Behr-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 44,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un es fwehtifchu\neefchanas Telti lihds ar to\nun es fwehtifchu arridsa\nnn nn winna Dehlus/\nmanni Preesteri effus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 45,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un es mittischu\nstarp Israēta Behrneem\nbuhſchu teem par Deew\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 46,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un teem buhſ at\nes tas KUNGS winn\nefinu/ kas Es tohs no\nSemmes iſweddıs efin\nwinnu Widdû dshwotu\nKUNGS/ winnu Dee\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta XXX. Noda\nTas Kwehpja-Altaris: 1. Weens\nliß no ifkurra dohdams par\nUppuri: 11. Tas Maṣagich\npreekſch teem Preestereem: 17-\nta Swaidischanas Efje: 22.\nKwehpja Sahlehm: 34.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ew buhſ arrid\nnu Kwehpja-A\nfiht pehz Kn\nnas/no Sittim-Kohka\nwinnu taiſiht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Weena Ohleks la\nna Gazums/ un ween\nwinna Plattums/ tſe\ngam buhſtam buht/ bet\nlektis tai irr winna A\nno ta paſcha buhſ win\nguem buht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tew buhſ win\nru Seltn pahrwilkt/wi-\ntu/ un winna Seena-\nkahrt/ ir winna Ragg\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tew buhſ win\n"
    }
  ],
